OL,3,CHuge cost of bin strikes to the
OL,4,Cenvironment as recycling rates plummet
OL,6,FThe scale of environmental damage
OL,7,Fcaused by the Birmingham bin strikes
OL,8,Fcan now be revealed, as figures
OL,9,Fobtained by ITV News Central show the
OL,10,Famount of rubbish being sent to
OL,11,Flandfill across the city has more than
OL,12,Fdoubled - while recycling rates have
OL,13,Falmost halved.
OL,15,FThe data shines a light on the wider
OL,16,Fproblems caused by the suspension of
OL,17,Fkerbside collections since the all-out
OL,18,Fstrikes began six months ago.
