OL,3,CHuge cost of bin strikes to the
OL,4,Cenvironment as recycling rates plummet
OL,6,FWazir Hussain has lived in the Alum
OL,7,FRock area for 20 years, and said the
OL,8,Fimpact had been "dreadful". He said
OL,9,Fhis neighbours were forced to put
OL,10,Frecycling in with normal waste, or
OL,11,Fdump it at roadsides, as the piles of
OL,12,Funcollected recycling mounted.
OL,14,F"It's very bad - just look at the
OL,15,Fstreet, it's all over the place," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,F"And we still have to pay council tax."
