OL,3,CHuge cost of bin strikes to the
OL,4,Cenvironment as recycling rates plummet
OL,6,FThe figures cover the first six months
OL,7,Fof this year, compared to the first
OL,8,Fsix months of 2024.
OL,10,FJohn Newson, the leading waste and
OL,11,Frecycling campaigner for Birmingham
OL,12,FFriends of the Earth, said it was a
OL,13,Fmatter of grave concern.
OL,15,F"Landfill is not a good thing," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,F"What we need is everything to go
OL,19,Fwhere it should go, where it can be
OL,20,Fmost used.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@_O]zD@AOU
