OL,3,CHuge cost of bin strikes to the
OL,4,Cenvironment as recycling rates plummet
OL,6,F"I'm certainly concerned that, people
OL,7,Fwho have been trying to separate their
OL,8,Fways to do the right thing might be
OL,9,Fgiving up, which is not what we want
OL,10,Fat all. We want everyone to have lots
OL,11,Fof confidence that when they separate
OL,12,Ftheir wastes, those waste will go to
OL,13,Fbe, recycled in an appropriate way."
OL,15,FWhat's more, the figures reveal that
OL,16,Fthe amount of waste recycled or sent
OL,17,Fto landfill actually only accounts for
OL,18,Faround 19% of the city's total waste
OL,19,Fload.
