OL,3,CHuge cost of bin strikes to the
OL,4,Cenvironment as recycling rates plummet
OL,6,FThe council told ITV News Central the
OL,7,Frest - in this case, 81% - would have
OL,8,Fbeen sent to energy recovery
OL,9,Ffacilities - ie incinerators, such as
OL,10,Fthe one in Tyseley.
OL,12,FBut official estimates from the IPCC
OL,13,F(Intergovernmental Panel on Climate
OL,14,FChange) suggest for every tonne of
OL,15,Fwaste burned, around a tonne of carbon
OL,16,Fdioxide is produced.
