OL,3,CHuge cost of bin strikes to the
OL,4,Cenvironment as recycling rates plummet
OL,6,FAnd yet, that seems to be where it's
OL,7,Fgoing.
OL,9,FIn response, Birmingham City Council's
OL,10,Fenvironment chief, Cllr Majid Mahmood,
OL,11,Fadmitted in a statement that the
OL,12,Fauthority needed to do better when it
OL,13,Fcomes to recycling.
