OL,3,CHuge cost of bin strikes to the
OL,4,Cenvironment as recycling rates plummet
OL,6,FHe added: "Due to industrial action we
OL,7,Fhave had to suspend the kerbside
OL,8,Frecycling collection but in order to
OL,9,Fsupport residents to recycle as much
OL,10,Fas possible we extended the opening
OL,11,Fhours of our household recycling
OL,12,Fcentres and the mobile waste centres,
OL,13,Fwith the latter focusing on hotspot
OL,14,Fareas.
