OL,3,CHuge cost of bin strikes to the
OL,4,Cenvironment as recycling rates plummet
OL,6,F"The council remains committed to our
OL,7,Fcarbon reduction ambitions, though the
OL,8,Fcity will achieve this through a range
OL,9,Fof activities beyond recycling such as
OL,10,Fretrofitting projects, support for
OL,11,Fbusinesses to become more energy
OL,12,Fefficient and improving the electric
OL,13,Fvehicle charging network."
OL,15,FThere is currently no date for when
OL,16,Frecycling collections might resume.
